import java.net.URL 
import scala.util.Try

val recordsDS = wetsRDD
 .flatMap { case (_, r) =>
   val content =  new String(r.getRecord().getContent(), "UTF-8")
   val uri = r.getRecord().getHeader().getTargetURI()
   Try {
      val url = new URL(uri)
      Record(uri, url.getHost, content)
   }.toOption
 }
 .toDS()
 .repartition(100)
 .filter { r =>
    isEnglishTextNaive(r.content)
 }
